# Biome (and the build tooling) expect LF. Without this, core.autocrlf=true on
# Windows materializes CRLF on checkout and `npm run lint` fails on a fresh
# clone. Keep everything LF in both the repo and the working tree.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
